Percentage changes in economic variables in the USA.

Source: R/data.R
us_change.Rd

us_change is a quarterly `tsibble` containing percentage changes in quarterly personal consumption expenditure, personal disposable income, production, savings and the unemployment rate for the US, 1970 to 2016.

Format

Time series of class `tsibble`

Source

Federal Reserve Bank of St Louis.

Examples


us_change
